gui.comment_under_title_pls_report:
Crashes usually occur from outdated or incompatible mods that you've added to the modpack.

Need help?
gui.comment_under_title: 1) Join Fabulously Optimized Discord. 2) Create a new post in #support, describe what you were doing before the crash. 3) Upload and copy the first log in the list below. 4) Paste the link to your support thread. 5) Wait for help. We'll tell you if we need more logs or other information.
